{"tid":893473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「有樓有高潮」Seasun拍三級片，露點片段網上瘋傳","createTime":"2018-11-07T15:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T06:31:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":162,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6b4a545c752bb50f4e9347f5975e58599c1b8f74","tid":893473,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2200000/2201088/fadd_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2200000%2F2201088%2Ffadd_600.jpeg&h=07994140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄧思宸（Seasun）於TVB節目《有樓萬事足》一句「有樓有高潮」，震撼全城，更被視為終極港女的典範！而最近Seasun又有機會再震驚大家，事關她豁出去接拍三級片《有罪》，該片以當年震撼中港台的李宗瑞性侵案作藍本，同Seasun一樣咁有話題性，雖然套戲仲未上映，不過近日網上竟流出疑似是Seasun的露點片段與照片，惹來不少網民評頭品足，「佢咁似個個Seasun嘅？佢唔係要釣金龜咩？點解咁慘要拍三級片呀？」「露點咁大犧牲，佢啲片酬夠唔夠買樓先？」而對於疑似露點片段於網上瘋傳，Seasun於facebook急急澄清：「本人嚴正聲明現時於網絡討論區上的所謂的流出照片並非本人，僅此表示會保留任何法律追究權利」<br />\n<br />\n全裸豁出去<br />\n<br />\n雖然條片同相都可能係假，不過今次Seasun為咗部戲真係豁出去架！第一次拍電影的她於戲中扮演陳少邦（飾演李宗瑞）女友，唔止三點盡露，更不乏不膽床戲，Seasun話：「拍攝時有做足安全措施，但今次我會三點盡露！（家人有無反對？）家人都擔心我，始終得自己一個人，好多事要小心啲。」Seasun又話自己對娛樂圈充滿好奇，希望大家多多支持及給予機會喎！<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2200000/2201088/hfg_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2200000%2F2201088%2Fhfg_600.jpg&h=41a56123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2200000/2201088/tgdg_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2200000%2F2201088%2Ftgdg_600.jpg&h=01c890c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0abde1f088430c435ecc0398253ad749350b4ac7","tid":893473,"uid":163500,"like":145,"dislike":0,"score":145,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:55:30.000Z","msg":"這麼醜的妞"},{"pid":"36a6164f3de4c94966562cc4490bfa4e3a94a022","tid":893473,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":198,"score":-198,"quote":{"pid":"0abde1f088430c435ecc0398253ad749350b4ac7","tid":893473,"uid":163500,"like":145,"dislike":0,"score":145,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:55:30.000Z","msg":"這麼醜的妞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:57:03.000Z","msg":"咁靚女都醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b53bd5c8247ddf349bd507fe0258c5b21f9897e","tid":893473,"uid":13421,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"送都唔屌"},{"pid":"d53949ae9f901e76868ac91544fa8a522e775078","tid":893473,"uid":91664,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"片呢？信唔信我屌埋你老母？"},{"pid":"dadaf441e807d1dc778e20b372485e571a979bd6","tid":893473,"uid":123264,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:58:10.000Z","msg":"如果我話佢d野唔係專燈炒作 有無人信?<br />\nbtw無人想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256bdceaad17c72854d55647ebd9cf6baa906cdb","tid":893473,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a82769f1d3388b3e89058d47828d45e0da300e7","tid":893473,"uid":210314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b4a545c752bb50f4e9347f5975e58599c1b8f74","tid":893473,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2200000/2201088/fadd_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2200000%2F2201088%2Ffadd_600.jpeg&h=07994140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄧思宸（Seasun）於TVB節目《有樓萬事足》一句「有樓有高潮」，震撼全城，更被視為終極港女的典範！而最近Seasun又有機會再震驚大家，事關她豁出去接拍三級片《有罪》，該片以當年震撼中港台的李宗瑞性侵案作藍本，同Seasun一樣咁有話題性，雖然套戲仲未上映，不過近日網上竟流出疑似是Seasun的露點片段與照片，惹來不少網民評頭品足，「佢咁似個個Seasun嘅？佢唔係要釣金龜咩？點解咁慘要拍三級片呀？」「露點咁大犧牲，佢啲片酬夠唔夠買樓先？」而對於疑似露點片段於網上瘋傳，Seasun於facebook急急澄清：「本人嚴正聲明現時於網絡討論區上的所謂的流出照片並非本人，僅此表示會保留任何法律追究權利」<br />\n<br />\n全裸豁出去<br />\n<br />\n雖然條片同相都可能係假，不過今次Seasun為咗部戲真係豁出去架！第一次拍電影的她於戲中扮演陳少邦（飾演李宗瑞）女友，唔止三點盡露，更不乏不膽床戲，Seasun話：「拍攝時有做足安全措施，但今次我會三點盡露！（家人有無反對？）家人都擔心我，始終得自己一個人，好多事要小心啲。」Seasun又話自己對娛樂圈充滿好奇，希望大家多多支持及給予機會喎！<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2200000/2201088/hfg_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2200000%2F2201088%2Fhfg_600.jpg&h=41a56123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2200000/2201088/tgdg_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2200000%2F2201088%2Ftgdg_600.jpg&h=01c890c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"好撚嘔心喔清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659aa5ba13e142767a241090285a6e9be2a2d57a","tid":893473,"uid":34080,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:00:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc691bce4e5bf09eebf170d7431bc7d8758e04f4","tid":893473,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:01:49.000Z","msg":"套戲好似仲有另一條女<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【李宗瑞事件翻拍成電影】36D姚琰欣被台仔寸：「這部戲每個女生都沒穿衣服，你也不例外」</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-10-29/656/20181029001441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-10-29%2F656%2F20181029001441.jpg&h=942ed369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n震驚社會的李宗瑞事件被翻拍成電影《有罪》，該戲去年9月殺青，其中，有著36D火辣身材的辣模姚琰欣(原名姚紫茵)也參與演出，在片中飾演李宗瑞的其中一名女友，而近來她接受港媒採訪，鬆口透露拍攝期間因不願進一步開放裸露尺度，竟遭工作人員酸言：「這部戲每個女生都沒穿衣服，你不是那個例外！」，讓她一度羞憤想辭演。<br />\n<br />\n身材火辣曾拍過寫真集的港模姚琰欣，參演李宗瑞事件翻拍電影《有罪》，近來她接受香港《蘋果》專訪，曝光了拍攝時發生的委屈情事，她透露當初看到腳色年齡要求跟她相符合，因此想搏一搏，試鏡後真的拿到該角色，也知道會被安排激烈床戲，需要一定程度的裸露，只是開拍定裝時，有某位負責服裝的男性工作人員拿了條丁字褲要她穿上，她委婉表示那場戲沒穿那麼露，沒想到被對方回嗆：「這部戲每個女生都沒穿衣服，你不是那個例外」。<br />\n<br />\n姚琰欣婉拒工作人員安排的裸露服裝，沒想到竟遭對方嗆聲羞辱，讓她當下感覺很受傷，因此立刻去跟導演表示想要辭演，導演進一步了解來龍去脈後，表示這只是場誤會，安撫後她才完成了拍攝，而姚琰欣完成該片拍攝後，竟發現男友也跟電影主角一樣，拿攝影機偷拍她，讓她傻眼直呼非常不被尊重，只能自嘲若是此事發生在接拍電影前，應該可以更融入角色吧。"},{"pid":"c4211b087d2004d4de526bf98e927c6913eed8df","tid":893473,"uid":197514,"like":5,"dislike":30,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe59648a43aef2289880df4d80c5ddf7df4ce3cd","tid":893473,"uid":10504,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:04:08.000Z","msg":"今次真係無興趣求片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有都唔好放出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c1a67fcb5d3c6403e8100dc25db3e26c6b0242","tid":893473,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"文字討論？連登真係越黎越有文學味道"},{"pid":"7214996c2daed790238f222f9e5b34afc3c5697f","tid":893473,"uid":34010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"唔想知，圖同片都咪放呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10cb41476e33dacfdbd11af654123c210283b04","tid":893473,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"其實佢ok，夠曬淫，同呢啲女屌閪會好爽"},{"pid":"7f93f5d26ee6fbb9a0c933d6fb14e4dd8bbe57dc","tid":893473,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"似炒作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fe466858cd57a95ccba8619885994fb32e59c3","tid":893473,"uid":192078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36a6164f3de4c94966562cc4490bfa4e3a94a022","tid":893473,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":198,"score":-198,"quote":{"pid":"0abde1f088430c435ecc0398253ad749350b4ac7","tid":893473,"uid":163500,"like":145,"dislike":0,"score":145,"citedB